{"tid":1870741,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[回力鏢]點解平時DC9打風唔跟表收錢，連登仔又話係資本主義自由市場??","createTime":"2020-02-09T05:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T10:33:28.000Z","uid":58335,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"567e800e2985ce76147a875453fbca8019f10b84","tid":1870741,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:01:39.000Z","msg":"平時炒樓、DC9打風唔跟表收錢<br />\n連登仔又話係資本主義自由市場??<br />\n<br />\n以前我話DC9打風唔跟表收錢犯法唔啱<br />\n連登仔講一大堆經濟理論，又話我唔識野又剩<br />\n一陣限制價格人地唔開工你連的士都冇得坐呀<br />\n冇錢你咪唔好坐囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但而家D人炒口罩又喊打喊殺<br />\n因為自己買唔到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一陣限制價格人地靚口罩都唔入<br />\n你連靚口罩都冇得用呀<br />\n冇錢你咪唔好買囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:冇炒"},{"pid":"43495df6b464b1956fa1a2625c9e1a6679bb7662","tid":1870741,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a9f2aa9254748970a7f1cc48a0d76d224dc66a8","tid":1870741,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:27:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211bbb8cc93537a047fcc05312435e1f505e2756","tid":1870741,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ced60c5bdc76dd379a51bb8b3e19a0d493deb2","tid":1870741,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa45dabc75fc259542e815c3544c8f6969882e3","tid":1870741,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T06:00:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84cd8177a0b75a1610a8a4482663d3b10d7144ef"